it out of his hand.

537
00:28:03,375 --> 00:28:04,671
I might have.

538
00:28:04,671 --> 00:28:05,756
How come?

539
00:28:05,756 --> 00:28:07,259
He was only 14.

540
00:28:07,259 --> 00:28:09,665
I mean, he's still not
old enough to drink.

